      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns exhibit-description">
          <p class="exhibit-description-main">With our exhibition <em>Art and Appetite</em>, we invite you to feast your eyes on the rich tradition of food and drink in American art with over 100 paintings, sculptures, and decorative arts from the 18th century to the 20th century. Continue the celebration of delectable edibles in your kitchen with our online cookbook featuring vintage American recipes featured in the exhibition as well as some scrumptious new offerings from Chicago's top culinary talent.</p>
          <p class="exhibit-description-link"><a href="http://www.artic.edu/exhibition/art-and-appetite-american-painting-culture-and-cuisine">Learn more about the exhibition.</a></p>
